# Traefik Configuration Rules

## Core Rules
- Installed through helm
- Use latest stable Traefik 3.x
- [install.sh](mdc:k8s/traefik/install.sh) its how to update

## Service Configuration
- Configuration file [values.yaml](mdc:k8s/traefik/values.yaml)
- Traefik Dashboard Exposed from home.server:31080
- HTTP services: Always Use path-based routing 
- TCP services (databases):
  - PostgreSQL: port 5432
  - Redis: port 6379
